data.description: Discover luxury living in the heart of Sedona Lakes, where this custom Coventry Homes masterpiece awaits. With 20-ft ceilings that greet you upon entry, the grandeur of this home is evident from the start. A wrought-iron rounded staircase adds a touch of elegance, while the gas fireplace in the living room provides warmth and charm.  Step outside to your private oasis, complete with a custom gunite pool, perfect for hot Texas summers. Entertain with ease in your outdoor kitchen and covered patio, creating memories under the open skies.  For peace of mind, this home features a full-size generator capable of powering the entire residence during outages. Experience the best of Sedona Lakes in this one-of-a-kind retreat, where luxury and functionality blend seamlessly. Your dream home awaits!
